"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wzk1665702797572.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wzk1665702797572.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wzk1665702797572.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wzk1665702797572\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Formats Library\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to define formats for drag and drop functionality.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__p_d6929e1_d6930e1_d6931e1\">Drag and drop formats define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon available when performing drag and drop actions in specific widgets.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__p_d6932e1_d6933e1_d6934e1\">The name of the format must be unique within the library and language definition, but it can be the same as a format in another library.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__section_bv4_gzf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d449558e61\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__ul_sys_gzf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3404e1_d3405e1_d3406e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3407e1_d3408e1_d3409e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cfv1665702708639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cfv1665702708639.html\" title=\"Language code for the global object with which you are working.\">Language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3410e1_d3411e1_d3412e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3413e1_d3414e1_d3415e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mzt1665702708708.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mzt1665702708708.html\" title=\"Default action when the selected object is dragged and dropped. Valid values are Copy, Move, or Create Shortcut. When the pop-up menu is displayed during a drag and drop action, the default action is shown in bold.\">Default Action</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3416e1_d3417e1_d3418e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ayn1665702708779.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ayn1665702708779.html\" title=\"Text to be displayed for the related action in the pop-up menu of the drag-and-drop format.\">Option Text</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3419e1_d3420e1_d3421e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fii1665702708857.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fii1665702708857.html\" title=\"Type of image to use as a background or icon—Glyph or File.\">Mouse Pointer Icon</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__li_d3422e1_d3423e1_d3424e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__section_zjh_hzf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d449558e149\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wzk1665702797572__p_d6941e1_d6942e1_d6943e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oqr1705583543910.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oqr1705583543910.html\" title=\"Drag-and-drop formats determine the actions and context menus for dragging and dropping objects in Tree and Picture widgets in desktop applications. They are maintained and deployed in a runtime library.\">Create and Maintain Drag-and-Drop Formats</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eav1719500059023.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag and Drop Behavior</a><p>Drag and drop behavior enables the user to select an object and drag it to another location with the mouse. When the mouse button is released, the selected object is copied, moved, or linked to by a shortcut.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swj1719500297780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533598\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533598\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Formats Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Formats Library Use this editor to define formats for drag and drop functionality. Drag and drop formats define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon available when performing drag and drop actions in specific widgets. The name of the format must be unique within the library and language definition, but it can be the same as a format in another library. Properties Name Language Description Default Action Option Text Mouse Pointer Icon Comments How to Create and Maintain Drag-and-Drop Formats Related Links Drag and Drop Behavior Drag and drop behavior enables the user to select an object and drag it to another location with the mouse. When the mouse button is released, the selected object is copied, moved, or linked to by a shortcut. Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}